e-mail: promed@promedmail.org

[This is a second indirect report of FMD in Kazakhstan, which has yet to
report any disease. Their last report to OIE was on 24 September 1999.
Kyrgyzia previously reported FMD on 12 February, 1999. - Mod.MHJ
